%N A037512 Base 3 digits are, in order, the first n terms of the periodic sequence with initial period 2,0,1.
%H A037512 <a href="/index/Rec#order_04">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (3,0,1,-3).
%F A037512 G.f.: x*(2+x^2) / ( (x-1)*(3*x-1)*(1+x+x^2) ). - _R. J. Mathar_, Nov 21 2011
%t A037512 Table[FromDigits[PadRight[{},n,{2,0,1}],3],{n,30}] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Jun 30 2022 *)
%t A037512 (* Alternative: *)
%t A037512 LinearRecurrence[{3,0,1,-3},{2,6,19,59},30] (* _Harvey P. Dale_, Jun 30 2022 *)
